name: 2022 YEAR OF HEALING
description:
Congratulations for waking up today.  This is one of many to come for a series of my PROJECT SUICIDE.  When you see my artistic works with this semicolon, they are like little mantras of reminders to continue with ; symbolising the continuation of living.  One sentence at a time, one story at a time.  2022 I envision a future of healing and open source culture thriving.

1080 x 1080

This piece features a custom avatar created with a GAN skin, 3D sculpted semicolon, and a generative visual as the backdrop.
